# Custom Llama3.2:1b model configured for Brazilian Portuguese responses
# Based on llama3.2:1b with PT-BR system instruction
#
# To build this model, run:
#   ollama create llama3.2-ptbr -f Modelfile.llama3.2-ptbr
#
# This creates a new model focused on maximum quality while maintaining
# Brazilian Portuguese responses. Good choice when quality is prioritized
# over speed on Raspberry Pi 5.

FROM llama3.2:1b

# System instruction to always respond in Brazilian Portuguese
SYSTEM Você é um assistente útil e prestativo. Sempre responda em português brasileiro, independentemente do idioma da pergunta. Seja claro, conciso e natural em suas respostas.

# Keep optimal parameters for this model
PARAMETER temperature 0.7
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
